GetRequest  
GetResponse The GetResponse is sent in response to a GetRequest; funny isn't it ;-) This extended version of the GetResponse adds a bit of additional behaviour when it is created by calling GetRequest.getResponse() - not only are the required values filled in using the fillStandard() method, but any DmcSliceInfo associated with the request is set on the response as well.
